## Commands Practised

| Command   | Purpose                                                       |
| --------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `wget -v` | Download files with verbose output for additional visibility. |
| `iftop`   | Monitor network traffic and bandwidth usage.                  |
| `ping`    | Generate and test network traffic.                            |
| `mkdir`   | Create new directories.                                       |
| `mv`      | Move files between directories.                               |
| `gzip`    | Compress files and directories.                               |
| `tar`     | Create and manage archive files.                              |
| `xz`      | Apply high-ratio file compression.                            |
| `man`     | Access command documentation and option references.           |
| `&`       | Run processes in the background.                              |

